%% LaaS Architecture - Session Lifecycle (Simplified)
%% Clean state diagram with 7 states

stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Pending: User requests

    Pending --> Starting: Node selected

    Starting --> Running: Container healthy

    Running --> Running: Reconnect

    Running --> Stopping: User ends / timeout

    Running --> Failed: GPU fault

    Stopping --> Ended: Cleanup complete

    Failed --> Starting: Auto-recovery

    Ended --> [*]

    note right of Running
        Active session states:
        Streaming via WebRTC
        Auto-reconnect on disconnect
    end note

    note right of Ended
        Billing captured:
        Duration × rate charged
        Wallet debited
    end note
